::Prowl/Striker/Zenyak::

Prowl creeps slowly through the hallways of the Ark after his target, 
Rampage. He raises his gun and aims it at the bot's head. He fires adn jumps 
forward, swinging his sword.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
A current sweeps across the two bots battling in the ocean. Too weak to 
resist, they are taken by the current away from the island and out into the 
ocean.
